channel.title: Where exactly would I find Pk-Isle-X
channel.description: Well, to make this not sound like a 'request'. I'm not asking if anyone would give it to me, or post a download link, but to 'hint' me in the direction of getting one. I've tried Google, r-s, and here. I cannot find it anywhere, actually, I did, in that server packet thing on r-s. But, it wasn't right, it was screwed up. So, if anyone has any idea on where to 'locate' it. Either post here or Pm me. Thanks guys. :) (and girls, if you help). :D
